The application will only access and share a user's last played song with the friends that the user has selected.

The application will not collect or store any personal information about the user or their friends, except for the information required to access and share the last played song.

The application will not use the user's last played song or any other data obtained from Deezer's API for any commercial purpose, including but not limited to targeted advertising.

The application will comply with all applicable laws and regulations, including but not limited to data protection and privacy laws.

The application will display the Deezer logo and attribution in accordance with Deezer's branding guidelines.

The application will provide a clear and accessible way for users to revoke access and delete their data, in accordance with Deezer's developer policies.

The application will not engage in any activity that may harm or disrupt Deezer's API or services, including but not limited to spamming, scraping, or distributing malware.

The application will be subject to periodic review by Deezer to ensure compliance with these terms of use and Deezer's developer policies.
